  &lt;span style="color: #BA36A5;"&gt;title&lt;/span&gt; =        {Competitive Growth of Scrutinyite (&lt;span style="color: #008000;"&gt;$\alpha$&lt;/span&gt;-PbO2) and Rutile
                  Polymorphs of \ce{SnO2} on All Orientations of Columbite
